  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Oxygen-Icons</title>

    <para>
      The <application>Oxygen-Icons</application> package contains the
      standard icon theme for <application>KDE Plasma 5</application>.
    </para>

    &lfs77_checked;

